cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

This paper focuses on zero-shot learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of semantic correlations and regularization, which are common topics in natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the experiments involve image classification, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
